explanation: The solution uses a recursive backtracking approach to generate all possible numbers. It explores all valid digit combinations at each position, ensuring the difference between consecutive digits is k. The time complexity is dominated by the number of possible combinations, while the space complexity is primarily due to the recursive call stack.

